Description:
    Creates a new Angular directive set up similar to an Angular 2 component

Example:
    yo yo:component thing [moduleName]

    This will create:
        app/components/thing/thing.js
        app/components/thing/thing.html
        app/components/thing/thing.scss

    If moduleName is passed this will create:
        app/moduleName/components/thing/thing.js
        app/moduleName/components/thing/thing.html
        app/moduleName/components/thing/thing.scss
